Barry Wilmore and Terry Virts recorded three spacewalks on GoPro cameras outside the International Space Station on February 25 and March 1 . 
  They were in preparation for the arrival of commercial spacecraft in 2017 . 
  The astronauts can be seen repairing the robotic arm of the space station and installing a new communication system . 
  Nasa recently signed a contract with SpaceX and Boeing . 
 